title: Grand Designs Australia S03E10 Clovelly House Revisited
description:
Grand Designs Australia - Season 3, Episode 10




Clovelly House Revisited

Host Peter Maddison revisits Julie and Patrick who fast tracked the construction of their super slick, ultra modern home in beachside Clovelly, thanks to a firm of pre-fab builders in Victoria. We learn how they've settled in and whether it's changed their lives for the better.




Original Air Date: 22-Apr-2013
